ision: stomp.\nPlacement Decision: image upper-center, captions lower third safe zone.\nTiming Events: - time:1.2 event:show image_1 - time:2.2 event:re-emphasize name\nTransition Out: soft fade\nEngagement Note: Name-image synchronization improves retention."}]}
