,\"end\":8.277},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"we're\",\"start\":8.277,\"end\":9.027},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"dancing\",\"start\":9.027,\"end\":9.777},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"and\",\"start\":9.777,\"end\":10.526},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"I'll\",\"start\":10.526,\"end\":11.276},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"choose\",\"start\":11.276,\"end\":12.026},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":12.026,\"end\":12.775},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"guy\",\"start\":12.775,\"end\":13.525},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"And\",\"start\":13.525,\"end\":14.275},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"tell\",\"start\":14.275,\"end\":15.025},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"us\",\"start\":15.025,\"end\":15.774},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":15.774,\"end\":16.524},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"reason\",\"start\":16.524,\"end\":17.274},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"we're\",\"start\":17.274,\"end\":18.023},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"facing\",\"start\":18.023,\"end\":18.773},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":18.773,\"end\":19.523},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"yoke\",\"start\":19.523,\"end\":20.272},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"If\",\"start\":20.272,\"end\":21.022},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"something's\",\"start\":21.022,\"end\":21.772},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"season\",\"start\":21.772,\"end\":22.521},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"and\",\"start\":22.521,\"end\":23.271},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":23.271,\"end\":24.021},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"lambs\",\"start\":24.021,\"end\":24.77},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"were\",\"start\":24.77,\"end\":25.52},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"on\",\"start\":25.52,\"end\":26.27},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":26.27,\"end\":27.019},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"road\",\"start\":27.019,\"end\":27.769},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"Searching\",\"start\":27.769,\"end\":28.519},{\"index\":38,\"text\":\"for\",\"start\":28.519,\"end\":29.268},{\"index\":39,\"text\":\"me\",\"start\":29.268,\"end\":30.018}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"Turn the page, maybe we'll find a brand new ending Where we're dancing and I'll choose that guy And tell us the reason we're facing the yoke If something's season and the lambs were on the road Searching for me\"}},\"text\":\"Turn the page, maybe we'll find a brand new ending Where we're dancing and I'll choose that guy And tell us the reason we're facing the yoke If something's season and the lambs were on the road Searching for me\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 30.018 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=serif, font_style=normal, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: starfield with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-30.018\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: maybe, we'll, brand.\nCaption Decision: placement=middle, animation=bounce_in, and grouped timings:\n- 0.031-2.280: \"Turn the page,\"\n- 2.280-4.529: \"maybe we'll find\"\n- 4.529-6.778: \"a brand new\"\n- 6.778-9.027: \"ending Where we're\"\n- 9.027-11.276: \"dancing and I'll\"\n- 11.276-13.525: \"choose that guy\"\n- 13.525-15.774: \"And tell us\"\n- 15.774-18.023: \"the reason we're\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.031 event: first caption appears\n- time: 30.018 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_012", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Create minimalist luxury captions with elegant serif style and soft motion. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0022.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":30.018},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0022.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":2.208,\"duration\":27.810000000000002},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":2.208,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":2.208,\"duration\":27.810000000000002},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"We\",\"start\":2.208,\"end\":2.94},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"all\",\"start\":2.94,\"end\":3.672},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"lost\",\"start\":3.672,\"end\":4.404},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"our\",\"start\":4.404,\"end\":5.135},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"stars\",\"start\":5.135,\"end\":5.867},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"Trying\",\"start\":5.867,\"end\":6.599},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":6.599,\"end\":7.331},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"light\",\"start\":7.331,\"end\":8.063},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"up\",\"start\":8.063,\"end\":8.795},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":8.795,\"end\":9.526},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"dark\",\"start\":9.526,\"end\":10.258},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"And\",\"start\":10.258,\"end\":10.99},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":10.99,\"end\":11.722},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"thought\",\"start\":11.722,\"end\":12.454},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":12.454,\"end\":13.186},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"saw\",\"start\":13.186,\"end\":13.917},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":13.917,\"end\":14.649},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"out\",\"start\":14.649,\"end\":15.381},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"there\",\"start\":15.381,\"end\":16.113},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"crying\",\"start\":16.113,\"end\":16.845},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"And\",\"start\":16.845,\"end\":17.577},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":17.577,\"end\":18.309},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"thought\",\"start\":18.309,\"end\":19.04},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":19.04,\"end\":19.772},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"heard\",\"start\":19.772,\"end\":20.504},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":20.504,\"end\":21.236},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"call\",\"start\":21.236,\"end\":21.968},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"my\",\"start\":21.968,\"end\":22.7},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"name\",\"start\":22.7,\"end\":23.431},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"And\",\"start\":23.431,\"end\":24.163},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":24.163,\"end\":24.895},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"thought\",\"start\":24.895,\"end\":25.627},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":25.627,\"end\":26.359},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"heard\",\"start\":26.359,\"end\":27.091},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":27.091,\"end\":27.822},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"out\",\"start\":27.822,\"end\":28.554},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"there\",\"start\":28.554,\"end\":29.286},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"crying\",\"start\":29.286,\"end\":30.018}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"We all lost our stars Trying to light up the dark And I thought I saw you out there crying And I thought I heard you call my name And I thought I heard you out there crying\"}},\"text\":\"We all lost our stars Trying to light up the dark And I thought I saw you out there crying And I thought I heard you call my name And I thought I heard you out there crying\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 30.018 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=modern_mono, font_style=italic, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: clean_black with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-30.018\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: stars, trying, light.\nCaption Decision: placement=top_safe, animation=impact, and grouped timings:\n- 2.208-5.135: \"We all lost our\"\n- 5.135-8.063: \"stars Trying to light\"\n- 8.063-10.990: \"up the dark And\"\n- 10.990-13.917: \"I thought I saw\"\n- 13.917-16.845: \"you out there crying\"\n- 16.845-19.772: \"And I thought I\"\n- 19.772-22.700: \"heard you call my\"\n- 22.700-25.627: \"name And I thought\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 2.208 event: first caption appears\n- time: 30.018 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_013", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Design energetic sports-reel captions with impact pops and high contrast. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0023.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":30.018},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0023.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.031,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"Oh,\",\"start\":0.031,\"end\":0.762},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"just\",\"start\":0.762,\"end\":1.494},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":1.494,\"end\":2.225},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"same.\",\"start\":2.225,\"end\":2.957},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"Oh,\",\"start\":2.957,\"end\":3.688},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"yeah,\",\"start\":3.688,\"end\":4.419},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"yeah,\",\"start\":4.419,\"end\":5.151},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"yeah,\",\"start\":5.151,\"end\":5.882},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"yeah,\",\"start\":5.882,\"end\":6.614},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"yeah,\",\"start\":6.614,\"end\":7.345},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"yeah.\",\"start\":7.345,\"end\":8.076},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"God,\",\"start\":8.076,\"end\":8.808},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"give\",\"start\":8.808,\"end\":9.539},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"us\",\"start\":9.539,\"end\":10.27},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":10.27,\"end\":11.002},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"reason\",\"start\":11.002,\"end\":11.733},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"for\",\"start\":11.733,\"end\":12.465},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":12.465,\"end\":13.196},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"this\",\"start\":13.196,\"end\":13.927},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"way.\",\"start\":13.927,\"end\":14.659},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"Say,\",\"start\":14.659,\"end\":15.39},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"I'm\",\"start\":15.39,\"end\":16.122},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"new\",\"start\":16.122,\"end\":16.853},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"here.\",\"start\":16.853,\"end\":17.584},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"It's\",\"start\":17.584,\"end\":18.316},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":18.316,\"end\":19.047},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"season.\",\"start\":19.047,\"end\":19.779},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"This\",\"start\":19.779,\"end\":20.51},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"land\",\"start\":20.51,\"end\":21.241},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"is\",\"start\":21.241,\"end\":21.973},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"on\",\"start\":21.973,\"end\":22.704},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":22.704,\"end\":23.435},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"road.\",\"start\":23.435,\"end\":24.167},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"Searching\",\"start\":24.167,\"end\":24.898},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"for\",\"start\":24.898,\"end\":25.63},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"meaning.\",\"start\":25.63,\"end\":26.361},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"But\",\"start\":26.361,\"end\":27.092},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"are\",\"start\":27.092,\"end\":27.824},{\"index\":38,\"text\":\"we\",\"start\":27.824,\"end\":28.555},{\"index\":39,\"text\":\"all\",\"start\":28.555,\"end\":29.287},{\"index\":40,\"text\":\"lost?\",\"start\":29.287,\"end\":30.018}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"Oh, just the same. Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah. God, give us the reason for you this way. Say, I'm new here. It's the season. This land is on the road. Searching for meaning. But are we all lost?\"}},\"text\":\"Oh, just the same. Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah. God, give us the reason for you this way. Say, I'm new here. It's the season. This land is on the road. Searching for meaning. But are we all lost?\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 30.018 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=sans, font_style=normal, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: parchment_dark with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-30.018\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: reason, season, searching.\nCaption Decision: placement=bottom_safe, animation=slide_up, and grouped timings:\n- 0.031-2.225: \"Oh, just the\"\n- 2.225-4.419: \"same. Oh, yeah,\"\n- 4.419-6.614: \"yeah, yeah, yeah,\"\n- 6.614-8.808: \"yeah, yeah. God,\"\n- 8.808-11.002: \"give us the\"\n- 11.002-13.196: \"reason for you\"\n- 13.196-15.390: \"this way. Say,\"\n- 15.390-17.584: \"I'm new here.\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.031 event: first caption appears\n- time: 30.018 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_014", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Use newsroom style captions: clean, authoritative, compact, and timed tightly. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0027.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":30.018},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0027.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":7.76,\"duration\":22.258000000000003},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":7.76,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":7.76,\"duration\":22.258000000000003},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"Yeah,\",\"start\":7.76,\"end\":8.244},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"yeah,\",\"start\":8.244,\"end\":8.728},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"yeah,\",\"start\":8.728,\"end\":9.212},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"yeah,\",\"start\":9.212,\"end\":9.695},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"yeah\",\"start\":9.695,\"end\":10.179},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"As\",\"start\":10.179,\"end\":10.663},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":10.663,\"end\":11.147},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"once,\",\"start\":11.147,\"end\":11.631},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"as\",\"start\":11.631,\"end\":12.115},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":12.115,\"end\":12.599},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"twice\