background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":18.239,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":18.239},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0032.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":18.208000000000002},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.031,\"t_end\":18.239,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":18.208000000000002},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"Now\",\"start\":0.031,\"end\":0.388},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":0.388,\"end\":0.745},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"take\",\"start\":0.745,\"end\":1.102},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"her\",\"start\":1.102,\"end\":1.459},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"out\",\"start\":1.459,\"end\":1.816},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"in\",\"start\":1.816,\"end\":2.173},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"your\",\"start\":2.173,\"end\":2.53},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"fancy\",\"start\":2.53,\"end\":2.887},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"car\",\"start\":2.887,\"end\":3.244},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"and\",\"start\":3.244,\"end\":3.601},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"make\",\"start\":3.601,\"end\":3.958},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"out\",\"start\":3.958,\"end\":4.315},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"in\",\"start\":4.315,\"end\":4.672},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":4.672,\"end\":5.029},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"rain\",\"start\":5.029,\"end\":5.386},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"And\",\"start\":5.386,\"end\":5.743},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"when\",\"start\":5.743,\"end\":6.1},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"she\",\"start\":6.1,\"end\":6.457},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"rings\",\"start\":6.457,\"end\":6.814},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":6.814,\"end\":7.171},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"up\",\"start\":7.171,\"end\":7.528},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"she\",\"start\":7.528,\"end\":7.885},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"know\",\"start\":7.885,\"end\":8.242},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"where\",\"start\":8.242,\"end\":8.599},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":8.599,\"end\":8.956},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"are\",\"start\":8.956,\"end\":9.314},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"but\",\"start\":9.314,\"end\":9.671},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":9.671,\"end\":10.028},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"know\",\"start\":10.028,\"end\":10.385},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"differently\",\"start\":10.385,\"end\":10.742},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"Now\",\"start\":10.742,\"end\":11.099},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"she\",\"start\":11.099,\"end\":11.456},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"sings\",\"start\":11.456,\"end\":11.813},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"along\",\"start\":11.813,\"end\":12.17},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"when\",\"start\":12.17,\"end\":12.527},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":12.527,\"end\":12.884},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"play\",\"start\":12.884,\"end\":13.241},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"guitar\",\"start\":13.241,\"end\":13.598},{\"index\":38,\"text\":\"making\",\"start\":13.598,\"end\":13.955},{\"index\":39,\"text\":\"brand\",\"start\":13.955,\"end\":14.312},{\"index\":40,\"text\":\"new\",\"start\":14.312,\"end\":14.669},{\"index\":41,\"text\":\"memories\",\"start\":14.669,\"end\":15.026},{\"index\":42,\"text\":\"Hope\",\"start\":15.026,\"end\":15.383},{\"index\":43,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":15.383,\"end\":15.74},{\"index\":44,\"text\":\"treat\",\"start\":15.74,\"end\":16.097},{\"index\":45,\"text\":\"her\",\"start\":16.097,\"end\":16.454},{\"index\":46,\"text\":\"better\",\"start\":16.454,\"end\":16.811},{\"index\":47,\"text\":\"than\",\"start\":16.811,\"end\":17.168},{\"index\":48,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":17.168,\"end\":17.525},{\"index\":49,\"text\":\"treated\",\"start\":17.525,\"end\":17.882},{\"index\":50,\"text\":\"me\",\"start\":17.882,\"end\":18.239}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"Now you take her out in your fancy car and make out in the rain And when she rings you up she know where you are but I know differently Now she sings along when you play guitar making brand new memories Hope you treat her better than you treated me\"}},\"text\":\"Now you take her out in your fancy car and make out in the rain And when she rings you up she know where you are but I know differently Now she sings along when you play guitar making brand new memories Hope you treat her better than you treated me\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 18.239 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=serif, font_style=normal, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: map_blue with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-18.239\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: fancy, rings, where.\nCaption Decision: placement=middle, animation=bounce_in, and grouped timings:\n- 0.031-1.102: \"Now you take\"\n- 1.102-2.173: \"her out in\"\n- 2.173-3.244: \"your fancy car\"\n- 3.244-4.315: \"and make out\"\n- 4.315-5.386: \"in the rain\"\n- 5.386-6.457: \"And when she\"\n- 6.457-7.528: \"rings you up\"\n- 7.528-8.599: \"she know where\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.031 event: first caption appears\n- time: 15.026 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_018", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Make social meme style captions with bouncy words and bright highlights. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0035.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":30.018},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0035.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.031,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"Have\",\"start\":0.031,\"end\":0.507},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":0.507,\"end\":0.983},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"got\",\"start\":0.983,\"end\":1.459},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"color\",\"start\":1.459,\"end\":1.935},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"in\",\"start\":1.935,\"end\":2.411},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"your\",\"start\":2.411,\"end\":2.887},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"cheeks?\",\"start\":2.887,\"end\":3.363},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"Do\",\"start\":3.363,\"end\":3.839},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":3.839,\"end\":4.315},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"ever\",\"start\":4.315,\"end\":4.791},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"get\",\"start\":4.791,\"end\":5.267},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":5.267,\"end\":5.743},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"feel\",\"start\":5.743,\"end\":6.219},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":6.219,\"end\":6.695},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"you've\",\"start\":6.695,\"end\":7.171},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"got?\",\"start\":7.171,\"end\":7.647},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"Shift\",\"start\":7.647,\"end\":8.123},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":8.123,\"end\":8.599},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"tide\",\"start\":8.599,\"end\":9.075},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":9.075,\"end\":9.551},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"sticks\",\"start\":9.551,\"end\":10.027},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"around\",\"start\":10.027,\"end\":10.503},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"like\",\"start\":10.503,\"end\":10.979},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"summits\",\"start\":10.979,\"end\":11.455},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"in\",\"start\":11.455,\"end\":11.931},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"your\",\"start\":11.931,\"end\":12.407},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"teeth?\",\"start\":12.407,\"end\":12.883},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"Are\",\"start\":12.883,\"end\":13.359},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"there\",\"start\":13.359,\"end\":13.835},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"some\",\"start\":13.835,\"end\":14.311},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"aces\",\"start\":14.311,\"end\":14.787},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"up\",\"start\":14.787,\"end\":15.262},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"your\",\"start\":15.262,\"end\":15.738},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"sleeve?\",\"start\":15.738,\"end\":16.214},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"Have\",\"start\":16.214,\"end\":16.69},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":16.69,\"end\":17.166},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"no\",\"start\":17.166,\"end\":17.642},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"idea\",\"start\":17.642,\"end\":18.118},{\"index\":38,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":18.118,\"end\":18.594},{\"index\":39,\"text\":\"you're\",\"start\":18.594,\"end\":19.07},{\"index\":40,\"text\":\"in\",\"start\":19.07,\"end\":19.546},{\"index\":41,\"text\":\"deep?\",\"start\":19.546,\"end\":20.022},{\"index\":42,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":20.022,\"end\":20.498},{\"index\":43,\"text\":\"dreamt\",\"start\":20.498,\"end\":20.974},{\"index\":44,\"text\":\"about\",\"start\":20.974,\"end\":21.45},{\"index\":45,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":21.45,\"end\":21.926},{\"index\":46,\"text\":\"nearly\",\"start\":21.926,\"end\":22.402},{\"index\":47,\"text\":\"every\",\"start\":22.402,\"end\":22.878},{\"index\":48,\"text\":\"night\",\"start\":22.878,\"end\":23.354},{\"index\":49,\"text\":\"this\",\"start\":23.354,\"end\":23.83},{\"index\":50,\"text\":\"week.\",\"start\":23.83,\"end\":24.306},{\"index\":51,\"text\":\"How\",\"start\":24.306,\"end\":24.782},{\"index\":52,\"text\":\"many\",\"start\":24.782,\"end\":25.258},{\"index\":53,\"text\":\"secrets\",\"start\":25.258,\"end\":25.734},{\"index\":54,\"text\":\"can\",\"start\":25.734,\"end\":26.21},{\"index\":55,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":26.21,\"end\":26.686},{\"index\":56,\"text\":\"keep?\",\"start\":26.686,\"end\":27.162},{\"index\":57,\"text\":\"Because\",\"start\":27.162,\"end\":27.638},{\"index\":58,\"text\":\"there's\",\"start\":27.638,\"end\":28.114},{\"index\":59,\"text\":\"this\",\"start\":28.114,\"end\":28.59},{\"index\":60,\"text\":\"tune\",\"start\":28.59,\"end\":29.066},{\"index\":61,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":29.066,\"end\":29.542},{\"index\":62,\"text\":\"found\",\"start\":29.542,\"end\":30.018}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"Have you got color in your cheeks? Do you ever get that feel that you've got? Shift the tide that sticks around like summits in your teeth? Are there some aces up your sleeve? Have you no idea that you're in deep? I dreamt about you nearly every night this week. How many secrets can you keep? Because there's this tune I found\"}},\"text\":\"Have you got color in your cheeks? Do you ever get that feel that you've got? Shift the tide that sticks around like summits in your teeth? Are there some aces up your sleeve? Have you no idea that you're in deep? I dreamt about you nearly every night this week. How many secrets can you keep? Because there's this tune I found\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 30.018 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=modern_mono, font_style=italic, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: starfield with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-30.018\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: color, cheeks, you've.\nCaption Decision: placement=top_safe, animation=impact, and grouped timings:\n- 0.031-1.935: \"Have you got color\"\n- 1.935-3.839: \"in your cheeks? Do\"\n- 3.839-5.743: \"you ever get that\"\n- 5.743-7.647: \"feel that you've got?\"\n- 7.647-9.551: \"Shift the tide that\"\n- 9.551-11.455: \"sticks around like summits\"\n- 11.455-13.359: \"in your teeth? Are\"\n- 13.359-15.262: \"there some aces up\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.031 event: first caption appears\n- time: 26.686 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_019", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Create devotional calm caption look with gentle fades and warm tones. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0036.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":30.018},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0036.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.031,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"Makes\",\"start\":0.031,\"end\":0.566},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"me\",\"start\":0.566,\"end\":1.102},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"think\",\"start\":1.102,\"end\":1.637},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"of\",\"start\":1.637,\"end\":2.173},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":2.173,\"end\":2.708},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"somehow\",\"start\":2.708,\"end\":3.244},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"When\",\"start\":3.244,\"end\":3.779},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":3.779,\"end\":4.315},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"play\",\"start\":4.315,\"end\":4.85},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"it\",\"start\":4.85,\"end\":5.386},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"on\",\"start\":5.386,\"end\":5.921},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"repeat\",\"start\":5.921,\"end\":6.457},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"Until\",\"start\":6.457,\"end\":6.992},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":6.992,\"end\":7.528},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"fall\",\"start\":7.528,\"end\":8.063},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"asleep\",\"start\":8.063,\"end\":8.599},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"Spilling\",\"start\":8.599,\"end\":9.134},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"drinks\",\"start\":9.134,\"end\":9.67},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"on\",\"start\":9.67,\"end\":10.205},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"my\",\"start\":10.205,\"end\":10.741},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"set\",\"start\":10.741,\"end\":11.276},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"seat\",\"start\":11.276,\"end\":11.812},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"Do\",\"start\":11.812,\"end\":12.347},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":12.347,\"end\":12.883},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"wanna\",\"start\":12.883,\"end\":13.418},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"know\",\"start\":13.418,\"end\":13.954},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"If\",\"start\":13.954,\"end\":14.489},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"this\",\"start\":14.489,\"end\":15.025},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"feeling\",\"start\":15.025,\"end\":15.56},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"flows\",\"start\":15.56,\"end\":16.095},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"both\",\"start\":16.095,\"end\":16.631},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"ways?\",\"start\":16.631,\"end\":17.166},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"Is\",\"start\":17.166,\"end\":17.702},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":17.702,\"end\":18.237},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":18.237,\"end\":18.773},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"see\",\"start\":18.773,\"end\":19.308},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"it\",\"start\":19.308,\"end\":19.844},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"all?\",\"start\":19.844,\"end\":20.379},{\"index\":38,\"text\":\"You\",\"start\":20.379,\"end\":20.915},{\"index\":39,\"text\":\"saw\",\"start\":20.915,\"end\":21.45},{\"index\":40,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":21.45,\"end\":21.986},{\"index\":41,\"text\":\"hope\",\"start\":21.986,\"end\":22.521},{\"index\":42,\"text\":\"in\",\"start\":22.521,\"end\":23.057},{\"index\":43,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":23.057,\"end\":23.592},{\"index\":44,\"text\":\"you'd\",\"start\":23.592,\"end\":24.128},{\"index\":45,\"text\":\"stay\",\"start\":24.128,\"end\":24.663},{\"index\":46,\"text\":\"Maybe\",\"start\":24.663,\"end\":25.199},{\"index\":47,\"text\":\"we\",\"start\":25.199,\"end\":25.734},{\"index\":48,\"text\":\"both\",\"start\":25.734,\"end\":26.27},{\"index\":49,\"text\":\"know\",\"start\":26.27,\"end\":26.805},{\"index\":50,\"text\":\"That\",\"start\":26.805,\"end\":27.341},{\"index\":51,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":27.341,\"end\":27.876},{\"index\":52,\"text\":\"nights\",\"start\":27.876,\"end\":28.412},{\"index\":53,\"text\":\"were\",\"start\":28.412,\"end\":28.947},{\"index\":54,\"text\":\"mainly\",\"start\":28.947,\"end\":29.483},{\"index\":55,\"text\":\"made\",\"start\":29.483,\"end\":30.018}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"Makes me think of you somehow When I play it on repeat Until I fall asleep Spilling drinks on my set seat Do I wanna know If this feeling flows both ways? Is that to see it all? You saw the hope in that you'd stay Maybe we both know That the nights were mainly made\"}},\"text\":\"Makes me think of you somehow When I play it on repeat Until I fall asleep Spilling drinks on my set seat Do I wanna know If this feeling flows both ways? Is that to see it all? You saw the hope in that you'd stay Maybe we both know That the nights were mainly made\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 30.018 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=sans, font_style=normal, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: clean_black with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-30.018\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: makes, think, somehow.\nCaption Decision: placement=bottom_safe, animation=slide_up, and grouped timings:\n- 0.031-1.637: \"Makes me think\"\n- 1.637-3.244: \"of you somehow\"\n- 3.244-4.850: \"When I play\"\n- 4.850-6.457: \"it on repeat\"\n- 6.457-8.063: \"Until I fall\"\n- 8.063-9.670: \"asleep Spilling drinks\"\n- 9.670-11.276: \"on my set\"\n- 11.276-12.883: \"seat Do I\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.031 event: first caption appears\n- time: 22.521 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_020", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Use sci-fi HUD caption design with mono font and precise timing. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0037.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":30.018},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0037.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.031,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"They're\",\"start\":0.031,\"end\":0.656},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"saying\",\"start\":0.656,\"end\":1.28},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"things\",\"start\":1.28,\"end\":1.905},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":1.905,\"end\":2.53},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":2.53,\"end\":3.155},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"can't\",\"start\":3.155,\"end\":3.779},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"say\",\"start\":3.779,\"end\":4.404},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"tomorrow\",\"start\":4.404,\"end\":5.029},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"day\",\"start\":5.029,\"end\":5.654},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"Crawling\",\"start\":5.654,\"end\":6.278},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"back\",\"start\":6.278,\"end\":6.903},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":6.903,\"end\":7.528},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":7.528,\"end\":8.152},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":8.152,\"end\":8.777},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"never\",\"start\":8.777,\"end\":9.402},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"thought\",\"start\":9.402,\"end\":10.027},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"I'd\",\"start\":10.027,\"end\":10.651},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"call\",\"start\":10.651,\"end\":11.276},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"and\",\"start\":11.276,\"end\":11.901},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"run\",\"start\":11.901,\"end\":12.526},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"If\",\"start\":12.526,\"end\":13.15},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":13.15,\"end\":13.775},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"knew,\",\"start\":13.775,\"end\":14.4},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"I'd\",\"start\":14.4,\"end\":15.025},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"not\",\"start\":15.025,\"end\":15.649},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"always\",\"start\":15.649,\"end\":16.274},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"knew\",\"start\":16.274,\"end\":16.899},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"Maybe\",\"start\":16.899,\"end\":17.523},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":17.523,\"end\":18.148},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"too,\",\"start\":18.148,\"end\":18.773},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"didn't\",\"start\":18.773,\"end\":19.398},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"even\",\"start\":19.398,\"end\":20.022},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"know\",\"start\":20.022,\"end\":20.647},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"what\",\"start\":20.647,\"end\":21.272},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":21.272,\"end\":21.897},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"fall\",\"start\":21.897,\"end\":22.521},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"for\",\"start\":22.521,\"end\":23.146},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"So\",\"start\":23.146,\"end\":23.771},{\"index\":38,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":23.771,\"end\":24.395},{\"index\":39,\"text\":\"knew,\",\"start\":24.395,\"end\":25.02},{\"index\":40,\"text\":\"now\",\"start\":25.02,\"end\":25.645},{\"index\":41,\"text\":\"I'm\",\"start\":25.645,\"end\":26.27},{\"index\":42,\"text\":\"going\",\"start\":26.27,\"end\":26.894},{\"index\":43,\"text\":\"through\",\"start\":26.894,\"end\":27.519},{\"index\":44,\"text\":\"Crawling\",\"start\":27.519,\"end\":28.144},{\"index\":45,\"text\":\"back\",\"start\":28.144,\"end\":28.769},{\"index\":46,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":28.769,\"end\":29.393},{\"index\":47,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":29.393,\"end\":30.018}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"They're saying things that you can't say tomorrow day Crawling back to you I never thought I'd call and run If I knew, I'd not always knew Maybe I too, didn't even know what to fall for So I knew, now I'm going through Crawling back to you\"}},\"text\":\"They're saying things that you can't say tomorrow day Crawling back to you I never thought I'd call and run If I knew, I'd not always knew Maybe I too, didn't even know what to fall for So I knew, now I'm going through Crawling back to you\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 30.018 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=serif, font_style=italic, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: parchment_dark with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-30.018\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: they're, saying, things.\nCaption Decision: placement=lower_third, animation=slide_left, and grouped timings:\n- 0.031-2.530: \"They're saying things that\"\n- 2.530-5.029: \"you can't say tomorrow\"\n- 5.029-7.528: \"day Crawling back to\"\n- 7.528-10.027: \"you I never thought\"\n- 10.027-12.526: \"I'd call and run\"\n- 12.526-15.025: \"If I knew, I'd\"\n- 15.025-17.523: \"not always knew Maybe\"\n- 17.523-20.022: \"I too, didn't even\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.031 event: first caption appears\n- time: 30.018 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_021", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Make captions neon cyber style with punchy motion and clear readability. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0038.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":28.162,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":28.162},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0038.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.959,\"duration\":27.203},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.959,\"t_end\":28.162,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.959,\"duration\":27.203},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"So\",\"start\":0.959,\"end\":1.503},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"have\",\"start\":1.503,\"end\":2.047},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":2.047,\"end\":2.591},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"got\",\"start\":2.591,\"end\":3.135},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":3.135,\"end\":3.679},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"guts\",\"start\":3.679,\"end\":4.223},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"Been\",\"start\":4.223,\"end\":4.767},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"wondering\",\"start\":4.767,\"end\":5.311},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"if\",\"start\":5.311,\"end\":5.856},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"your\",\"start\":5.856,\"end\":6.4},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"heart's\",\"start\":6.4,\"end\":6.944},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"still\",\"start\":6.944,\"end\":7.488},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"open\",\"start\":7.488,\"end\":8.032},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"And\",\"start\":8.032,\"end\":8.576},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"if\",\"start\":8.576,\"end\":9.12},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"so,\",\"start\":9.12,\"end\":9.664},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":9.664,\"end\":10.208},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"wanna\",\"start\":10.208,\"end\":10.752},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"know\",\"start\":10.752,\"end\":11.296},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"what\",\"start\":11.296,\"end\":11.84},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"time\",\"start\":11.84,\"end\":12.384},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"it\",\"start\":12.384,\"end\":12.928},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"should\",\"start\":12.928,\"end\":13.472},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"Simmer\",\"start\":13.472,\"end\":14.016},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"down,\",\"start\":14.016,\"end\":14.56},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"I'm\",\"start\":14.56,\"end\":15.105},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"poker\",\"start\":15.105,\"end\":15.649},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"up\",\"start\":15.649,\"end\":16.193},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"I'm\",\"start\":16.193,\"end\":16.737},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"sorry\",\"start\":16.737,\"end\":17.281},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":17.281,\"end\":17.825},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"interrupt,\",\"start\":17.825,\"end\":18.369},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"it's\",\"start\":18.369,\"end\":18.913},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"just\",\"start\":18.913,\"end\":19.457},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"I'm\",\"start\":19.457,\"end\":20.001},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"constantly\",\"start\":20.001,\"end\":20.545},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"on\",\"start\":20.545,\"end\":21.089},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":21.089,\"end\":21.633},{\"index\":38,\"text\":\"course\",\"start\":21.633,\"end\":22.177},{\"index\":39,\"text\":\"I've\",\"start\":22.177,\"end\":22.721},{\"index\":40,\"text\":\"tried\",\"start\":22.721,\"end\":23.265},{\"index\":41,\"text\":\"In\",\"start\":23.265,\"end\":23.81},{\"index\":42,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":23.81,\"end\":24.354},{\"index\":43,\"text\":\"kiss\",\"start\":24.354,\"end\":24.898},{\"index\":44,\"text\":\"you,\",\"start\":24.898,\"end\":25.442},{\"index\":45,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":25.442,\"end\":25.986},{\"index\":46,\"text\":\"don't\",\"start\":25.986,\"end\":26.53},{\"index\":47,\"text\":\"know\",\"start\":26.53,\"end\":27.074},{\"index\":48,\"text\":\"if\",\"start\":27.074,\"end\":27.618},{\"index\":49,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":27.618,\"end\":28.162}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"So have you got the guts Been wondering if your heart's still open And if so, I wanna know what time it should Simmer down, I'm poker up I'm sorry to interrupt, it's just I'm constantly on the course I've tried In to kiss you, I don't know if you\"}},\"text\":\"So have you got the guts Been wondering if your heart's still open And if so, I wanna know what time it should Simmer down, I'm poker up I'm sorry to interrupt, it's just I'm constantly on the course I've tried In to kiss you, I don't know if you\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 28.162 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=modern_mono, font_style=normal, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: neutral_dark with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-28.162\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: wondering, heart's, still.\nCaption Decision: placement=left_lower, animation=slide_right, and grouped timings:\n- 0.959-2.591: \"So have you\"\n- 2.591-4.223: \"got the guts\"\n- 4.223-5.856: \"Been wondering if\"\n- 5.856-7.488: \"your heart's still\"\n- 7.488-9.120: \"open And if\"\n- 9.120-10.752: \"so, I wanna\"\n- 10.752-12.384: \"know what time\"\n- 12.384-14.016: \"it should Simmer\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.959 event: first caption appears\n- time: 23.810 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_022", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Create minimalist luxury captions with elegant serif style and soft motion. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0039.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":30.001,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":30.001},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0039.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":10.561,\"duration\":19.44},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":10.561,\"t_end\":30.001,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":10.561,\"duration\":19.44},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"If\",\"start\":10.561,\"end\":11.086},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":11.086,\"end\":11.612},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"want\",\"start\":11.612,\"end\":12.137},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"it\",\"start\":12.137,\"end\":12.663},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"soon,\",\"start\":12.663,\"end\":13.188},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"I\",\"start\":13.188,\"end\":13.713},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"want\",\"start\":13.713,\"end\":14.239},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":14.239,\"end\":14.764},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"know\",\"start\":14.764,\"end\":15.29},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"If\",\"start\":15.29,\"end\":15.815},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"this\",\"start\":15.815,\"end\"