t\":25.645,\"end\":26.27},{\"index\":42,\"text\":\"it\",\"start\":26.27,\"end\":26.894},{\"index\":43,\"text\":\"through\",\"start\":26.894,\"end\":27.519},{\"index\":44,\"text\":\"Crawling\",\"start\":27.519,\"end\":28.144},{\"index\":45,\"text\":\"back\",\"start\":28.144,\"end\":28.769},{\"index\":46,\"text\":\"to\",\"start\":28.769,\"end\":29.393},{\"index\":47,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":29.393,\"end\":30.018}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"Made for saying things that you can't say tomorrow day Crawling back to you And the hope of coming when You better feel like you're always through Maybe I'm too busy Maybe you want to fall for somebody new Now I've bought it through Crawling back to you\"}},\"text\":\"Made for saying things that you can't say tomorrow day Crawling back to you And the hope of coming when You better feel like you're always through Maybe I'm too busy Maybe you want to fall for somebody new Now I've bought it through Crawling back to you\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 30.018 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=serif, font_style=normal, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: cinematic_red with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-30.018\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: saying, things, can't.\nCaption Decision: placement=middle, animation=bounce_in, and grouped timings:\n- 0.031-1.905: \"Made for saying\"\n- 1.905-3.779: \"things that you\"\n- 3.779-5.654: \"can't say tomorrow\"\n- 5.654-7.528: \"day Crawling back\"\n- 7.528-9.402: \"to you And\"\n- 9.402-11.276: \"the hope of\"\n- 11.276-13.150: \"coming when You\"\n- 13.150-15.025: \"better feel like\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.031 event: first caption appears\n- time: 26.270 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
{"task": "planner_text", "id": "planner_song_style_024", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are VASP Planner. Return ONLY EDIT PLAN text with exact headings. No JSON. No markdown."}, {"role": "user", "content": "Task: Generate a structured language edit plan for a short-form video. User Instruction: Use newsroom style captions: clean, authoritative, compact, and timed tightly. Keep captions synced exactly to song chunk song_0041.m4a. Goal: Create a smooth, engaging, high-retention edit using the provided elements. Priority Order: [Audio, Caption, Image, Video, Sfx, Gif] Rules: - Start from an empty video canvas. - Use the main audio as the full timeline backbone. - Divide the video into meaningful segments using caption timing, topic changes, silence, emphasis, and pacing. - Segments may be caption-focused, visual-focused, transition-focused, or mixed. - Keep captions readable at all times. - Never let visuals cover important captions. - Keep one consistent style across the full video unless a strong moment needs extra emphasis. - Highlight the currently spoken caption word. - Correct a caption word only if it is clearly wrong and the intended word is obvious from context. - Use images, videos, gifs, SFX, and music only when they match the spoken topic or improve the edit. - Prefer showing media exactly when the related topic, object, person, or event is mentioned. - Each element may contain: - about = what the element contains or represents - aim = preferred use of the element - Prefer aim over about if both exist. Either may be empty. - If aim exists, try to satisfy it unless it strongly harms the edit. - If there is no good media match, keep the segment caption-focused. - Use position, crop, scale, transitions, zoom, motion, glow, entrance, exit, split layout, background color, gradient, blur, or design treatment only when they improve clarity, engagement, or flow. - Use SFX only on important words, transitions, punchlines, or impact moments. - Keep background music below speech when both are present. - Maximize engagement, readability, relevance, smoothness, and retention. You should be able to decide the time duration where multiple caption should be placed on the screen at once, along with which word is important and what to color and highlight Elements:\n{\"version\":\"1.0\",\"video\":{\"size\":{\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"fps\":30,\"bg_color\":[0,0,0],\"output_path\":\"output/a2v_video.mp4\"},\"elements\":[{\"element_id\":\"audio_1\",\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.0,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"play\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"music\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.0,\"duration\":30.018},\"source_uri\":\"assets/inputs/song_0041.m4a\",\"loop\":true,\"volume\":1.0,\"trim_in\":0.0}},{\"element_id\":\"caption_track_1\",\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"actions\":[{\"t_start\":0.031,\"t_end\":30.018,\"op\":\"show\",\"params\":{}}],\"properties\":{\"type\":\"caption\",\"timing\":{\"start\":0.031,\"duration\":29.987000000000002},\"transform\":{\"x\":540.0,\"y\":1660.0,\"scale_x\":1.0,\"scale_y\":1.0,\"rotation_deg\":0.0,\"opacity\":1.0,\"anchor\":\"center\",\"size\":{},\"flip_x\":false,\"flip_y\":false},\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"asr_whisperx\",\"caption_mode\":\"single_combined_element\",\"word_timing_map\":[{\"index\":0,\"text\":\"If\",\"start\":0.031,\"end\":0.762},{\"index\":1,\"text\":\"this\",\"start\":0.762,\"end\":1.494},{\"index\":2,\"text\":\"feeling\",\"start\":1.494,\"end\":2.225},{\"index\":3,\"text\":\"flows\",\"start\":2.225,\"end\":2.957},{\"index\":4,\"text\":\"away\",\"start\":2.957,\"end\":3.688},{\"index\":5,\"text\":\"Without\",\"start\":3.688,\"end\":4.419},{\"index\":6,\"text\":\"opening\",\"start\":4.419,\"end\":5.151},{\"index\":7,\"text\":\"that\",\"start\":5.151,\"end\":5.882},{\"index\":8,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":5.882,\"end\":6.614},{\"index\":9,\"text\":\"stay\",\"start\":6.614,\"end\":7.345},{\"index\":10,\"text\":\"Or\",\"start\":7.345,\"end\":8.076},{\"index\":11,\"text\":\"at\",\"start\":8.076,\"end\":8.808},{\"index\":12,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":8.808,\"end\":9.539},{\"index\":13,\"text\":\"nights\",\"start\":9.539,\"end\":10.27},{\"index\":14,\"text\":\"when\",\"start\":10.27,\"end\":11.002},{\"index\":15,\"text\":\"they\",\"start\":11.002,\"end\":11.733},{\"index\":16,\"text\":\"would\",\"start\":11.733,\"end\":12.465},{\"index\":17,\"text\":\"make\",\"start\":12.465,\"end\":13.196},{\"index\":18,\"text\":\"the\",\"start\":13.196,\"end\":13.927},{\"index\":19,\"text\":\"same\",\"start\":13.927,\"end\":14.659},{\"index\":20,\"text\":\"things\",\"start\":14.659,\"end\":15.39},{\"index\":21,\"text\":\"But\",\"start\":15.39,\"end\":16.122},{\"index\":22,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":16.122,\"end\":16.853},{\"index\":23,\"text\":\"can't\",\"start\":16.853,\"end\":17.584},{\"index\":24,\"text\":\"say\",\"start\":17.584,\"end\":18.316},{\"index\":25,\"text\":\"it's\",\"start\":18.316,\"end\":19.047},{\"index\":26,\"text\":\"a\",\"start\":19.047,\"end\":19.779},{\"index\":27,\"text\":\"matter\",\"start\":19.779,\"end\":20.51},{\"index\":28,\"text\":\"of\",\"start\":20.51,\"end\":21.241},{\"index\":29,\"text\":\"days\",\"start\":21.241,\"end\":21.973},{\"index\":30,\"text\":\"You\",\"start\":21.973,\"end\":22.704},{\"index\":31,\"text\":\"are\",\"start\":22.704,\"end\":23.435},{\"index\":32,\"text\":\"born\",\"start\":23.435,\"end\":24.167},{\"index\":33,\"text\":\"alone\",\"start\":24.167,\"end\":24.898},{\"index\":34,\"text\":\"You\",\"start\":24.898,\"end\":25.63},{\"index\":35,\"text\":\"can\",\"start\":25.63,\"end\":26.361},{\"index\":36,\"text\":\"do\",\"start\":26.361,\"end\":27.092},{\"index\":37,\"text\":\"what\",\"start\":27.092,\"end\":27.824},{\"index\":38,\"text\":\"you\",\"start\":27.824,\"end\":28.555},{\"index\":39,\"text\":\"lost\",\"start\":28.555,\"end\":29.287},{\"index\":40,\"text\":\"before\",\"start\":29.287,\"end\":30.018}],\"transcript\":{\"full_text\":\"If this feeling flows away Without opening that you stay Or at the nights when they would make the same things But you can't say it's a matter of days You are born alone You can do what you lost before\"}},\"text\":\"If this feeling flows away Without opening that you stay Or at the nights when they would make the same things But you can't say it's a matter of days You are born alone You can do what you lost before\",\"language\":\"en\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"line_height\":1.2,\"letter_spacing\":0.0,\"wrap\":true,\"padding\":{\"top\":0.0,\"right\":0.0,\"bottom\":0.0,\"left\":0.0},\"background_opacity\":0.0,\"stroke_width\":0.0}}],\"serializer_mode\":\"v2\"}\nOutput: Return ONLY the following structure: EDIT PLAN Global Style: Audio Decision: Caption Style: Visual Style: Background Style: Segmentation Rule: Segment 1 Time: Purpose: Elements Used: Caption Decision: Visual Decision: Animation Decision: Placement Decision: Timing Events: - time: event Transition Out: Engagement Note: Segment 2 ... Repeat for all segments. Constraints: - Do NOT return JSON. - Do NOT return code. - Do NOT explain reasoning. - Use exact element ids and times whenever possible. - Keep the exact same headings every time. - Make the result easy to convert into JSON later."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "EDIT PLAN\nGlobal Style: Dynamic caption-focused short with style-driven typography and motion.\nAudio Decision: Use audio_1 from 0.000 to 30.018 as backbone at full volume.\nCaption Style: font_family=modern_mono, font_style=italic, white base, gold inline highlights only for important words.\nVisual Style: Caption-only design test with animated entrances and no image overlays.\nBackground Style: map_blue with timed subtle design overlays.\nSegmentation Rule: Group transcript into 3-4 word caption blocks using mapping_json timings exactly.\nSegment 1\nTime: 0.000-30.018\nPurpose: Validate caption sync + style diversity on real song chunk mapping.\nElements Used: audio_1, caption_track_1\nCaption Decision: Important Words: feeling, flows, without.\nCaption Decision: placement=top_safe, animation=impact, and grouped timings:\n- 0.031-2.957: \"If this feeling flows\"\n- 2.957-5.882: \"away Without opening that\"\n- 5.882-8.808: \"you stay Or at\"\n- 8.808-11.733: \"the nights when they\"\n- 11.733-14.659: \"would make the same\"\n- 14.659-17.584: \"things But you can't\"\n- 17.584-20.510: \"say it's a matter\"\n- 20.510-23.435: \"of days You are\"\nVisual Decision: Keep text readable and avoid clipping within 9:16 safe area.\nAnimation Decision: Animate each caption entry with chosen style and hold until next phrase.\nPlacement Decision: Use caption safe zone with translucent panel behind text.\nTiming Events:\n- time: 0.031 event: first caption appears\n- time: 30.018 event: last caption exits\nTransition Out: short fade.\nEngagement Note: Strong typography + motion variety while preserving sync accuracy."}]}
